    + Added simple test to demonstrate new .HRB feature

2004-08-01 14:00 UTC-3 Marcelo Lombardo <marcelo@xharbour.com.br>
  * source/vm/runner.c
    ! HRB file loading process very optimized. Now it works on a memory
      buffer, not with a file handle.
    + Added hb_hrbLoadFromFile() function.
    - Removed useless (due to above change) file management functions.
    ! __HRBLOAD() can now receive as parameter either a file name or
      a string variable with the HRB body. It recognizes HRB header
      signature and call hb_hrbLoad() or hb_hrbLoadFromFile() properly.

