2004-07-27 15:15 UTC+0200 Przemyslaw Czerpak (druzus/at/priv.onet.pl)
  * xharbour/bin/hb-func.sh
  * xharbour/config/global.cf
    * added HB_DB_DRVEXT env var which may containt additional DB drivers

  * xharbour/include/dbinfo.ch
